attributes.description: Agentcore browser dashboard showcasing browser automation sessions, user takeover events, and stream connection operations.

params.markdown:
## Browser

This dashboard provides insights into the following:

- Browser session lifecycle metrics including sessions started, stopped, and average duration
- User takeover monitoring with takeover counts, durations, and release events
- Browser automation stream connection performance, errors, and throttling
- Browser session start operations with duration, errors, and throttle analysis

query.esql:
FROM metrics-aws_bedrock_agentcore.metrics-default
| WHERE @timestamp > ?_tstart AND @timestamp < ?_tend
| where aws.dimensions.Operation == "StartBrowserSession" AND aws.dimensions.Resource IS NOT NULL
| STATS sum_start_browser_sessions = sum(aws.bedrock_agentcore.metrics.Invocations.sum)

FROM metrics-aws_bedrock_agentcore.metrics-default
| WHERE @timestamp > ?_tstart AND @timestamp < ?_tend
| where aws.dimensions.Operation == "StartBrowserSession" AND aws.dimensions.Resource IS NOT NULL
| STATS sum_start_browser_sessions = sum(aws.bedrock_agentcore.metrics.Invocations.sum)

embeddableConfig.description: Total number of browser sessions initiated in AWS Bedrock AgentCore.

query.esql:
FROM metrics-aws_bedrock_agentcore.metrics-default
| WHERE @timestamp > ?_tstart AND @timestamp < ?_tend
| WHERE aws.dimensions.Operation == "ConnectBrowserAutomationStream"
  AND aws.dimensions.Resource IS NOT NULL
| STATS sum_user_errors = sum(aws.bedrock_agentcore.metrics.UserErrors.sum),
        sum_system_errors = sum(aws.bedrock_agentcore.metrics.SystemErrors.sum),
        avg_duration = avg(aws.bedrock_agentcore.metrics.Duration.avg), 
        sum_throttles = sum(aws.bedrock_agentcore.metrics.Throttles.sum),
        sum_invocations = sum(aws.bedrock_agentcore.metrics.Invocations.sum) by aws.dimensions.Resource
| EVAL total_errors = sum_system_errors + sum_user_errors        
| SORT total_errors DESC
| LIMIT 10

FROM metrics-aws_bedrock_agentcore.metrics-default
| WHERE @timestamp > ?_tstart AND @timestamp < ?_tend
| WHERE aws.dimensions.Operation == "ConnectBrowserAutomationStream"
  AND aws.dimensions.Resource IS NOT NULL
| STATS sum_user_errors = sum(aws.bedrock_agentcore.metrics.UserErrors.sum),
        sum_system_errors = sum(aws.bedrock_agentcore.metrics.SystemErrors.sum),
        avg_duration = avg(aws.bedrock_agentcore.metrics.Duration.avg), 
        sum_throttles = sum(aws.bedrock_agentcore.metrics.Throttles.sum),
        sum_invocations = sum(aws.bedrock_agentcore.metrics.Invocations.sum) by aws.dimensions.Resource
| EVAL total_errors = sum_system_errors + sum_user_errors        
| SORT total_errors DESC
| LIMIT 10

attributes.title: sum_user_errors & sum_system_errors & avg_duration & sum_throttles & sum_invocations of (empty)
